{"tid":1267800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［投票］［值得討論］龍和道 / 愛丁堡：灣仔唔夠人！","createTime":"2019-06-30T05:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T12:14:27.000Z","uid":66390,"like":56,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"890c60bdf5e8b0f1fb205d3629394b8738e05f55","tid":1267800,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:25:27.000Z","msg":"開始有唔同人組織聽日<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兩大行動</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 龍和道 一齊同林鄭睇升旗<br />\n2. 自己掛黑旗<br />\n<br />\n好老實 我一定會去灣仔<br />\n雖然大家都知警狗<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佈左水馬陣</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但真係會入唔到咩？</span><br />\n你地諗一個問題<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">車同觀眾點入 我地就可以點衝</span><br />\n就算唔得 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人多 咪同佢硬碰硬</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟各自爬山 掛黑旗都係抗議方式 </span><br />\n但掛撚完 轉個頭一散就會拆 唔會有好大既noise <br />\n相反 <span style=\"color: red;\">同林鄭一齊睇升旗 爆唔撚到入去 但有大型衝突 個noise點都大啲</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我只係唔想灣仔無人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">衝 物資組 first aid 請到灣仔</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">極和理非 可以選擇愛丁堡</span><br />\n<br />\n但大家諗下 6.21圍警狗個人數<br />\n都未必夠聽日睇升旗<br />\n真係需要搞愛丁堡咩？要搞 少少人就夠<br />\n所以大家睇投票方向做人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">投票時間</span> 唔係決定去邊<br />\n而係比大家一個方向 人數傾向<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FBvF33N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFBvF33N.png&h=116cc62a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5XkF33O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5XkF33O.png&h=57277cc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />龍和道 進佔升旗禮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愛丁堡 黑色升旗禮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗住去完愛丁堡睇情況再來<br />\n唔好諗住睇新聞咩情況再出門口<br />\n聽日一定要準時到達！<br />\n聽日時間緊逼"},{"pid":"4969fd705b13fb0d1f4bf27ab7be4b9786e9c31f","tid":1267800,"uid":66390,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:26:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓豬建議： 聽日0630準時到灣仔</span>"},{"pid":"1b47b9c1282cb432533d43b89777eb18dba61f25","tid":1267800,"uid":3456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:26:21.000Z","msg":"71不舉後食偉哥建議<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dcdAfS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dcdAfS</a>"},{"pid":"ec4dd649246a8a3e09722c9d1b535739c74aeb7e","tid":1267800,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:27:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161fbbd3790ef9bb75e41a5bf70fd15a5d8342ab","tid":1267800,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yn7ASQz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYn7ASQz.jpg&h=551baa69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d6f40441d02b7abd376dc7d0b56b8ac2ddfb6bf","tid":1267800,"uid":66390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:29:28.000Z","msg":"但相反<br />\n去完灣仔睇情況 再退守落愛丁堡係可以<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以點都要去左灣仔先</span>"},{"pid":"adce74de8379a076589e06754c54bc078c082947","tid":1267800,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691a598e67ee38e81943bf2b844cb7962ba34df5","tid":1267800,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05